The paper deals with a nonparametric problem of detecting anomalies in a network, which involves statistical learning and inference. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.ST (Statistics). The paper also involves information theory and signal processing, which makes cs.IT (Information Theory) a likely category. Finally, the paper deals with network analysis and communication, which makes cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) a possible category.
